---
title: Creamy Tarragon Lobster and Shrimp Ravioli with Lemony Panko Topping
description: This luxurious lobster-stuffed ravioli dish is full of succulent shrimp and smothered in a creamy tarragon sauce. Baby spinach, hearty zucchini and a lemony panko topping complete this show-stopping meal.
